name                py-cftime
revision            0

categories-append   devel
license             MIT
maintainers         {reneeotten @reneeotten} openmaintainer

description         Time-handling functionality from netcdf4-python
long_description    ${description}

checksums           rmd160  376c494e370563a04d079a06d3d72f6400c965ae \
                    sha256  53fd3204c89d1e20e599995c074c92d7cbed09962252ad842dd90ca2f9ce5f5f \
